Introduction
============
The Flash Mini Slideshow lets you embedd a small flash movie in you website that displays any number of
images in a slideshow.

Demo
====
To see the slideshow in action, open index.html in your browser.

Installing/configuring
======================
To see how to use the slideshow, have a look at slides.txt.

More information
================
Comments and suggestions to alistair@codebrane.com
